    {
      "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8087-9e41-d17f23b2c89c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "PredictCS automatically flags students at risk and sends them feedback useful for early intervention. It uses multi-modal data as inputs for multiple predictive models - prior academic performance, carachteristics, logs and student progress. The model generates predictions every week. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8087-9e41-d17f23b2c89c",
        "parent": {
